AUTOBOLI LTD

At AUTOBOLI LTD, we specialize in collecting comprehensive auction data from across the UK and delivering it directly to dealers and traders. Our subscription-based service provides up-to-date and accurate insights from a wide range of auctions, ensuring that our clients are always ahead in the competitive automotive market.

With a commitment to transparency and efficiency, we empower businesses with the data they need to make informed purchasing decisions. Whether you’re a local dealer or a national trader, AUTOBOLI LTD is your trusted partner for auction data intelligence.

Comprehensive Vehicle Information

Each auction listing includes detailed vehicle data to help you evaluate potential purchases. You’ll get:

Make, model, and year of the vehicle.
Condition reports detailing any issues or damage.
Mileage and other important specs.
Starting and current bids to monitor price trends.

Having this level of detail allows you to make informed bids and find the best deals for your inventory.

  • How It Works

Start accessing auctions in three simple steps.

Start accessing auctions in three simple steps.

Sign Up and Get Started

Choose the perfect subscription plan—Silver, Gold, or Platinum—and sign up in minutes. Each plan offers tailored benefits to unlock real-time auction data. Start transforming how you navigate the auction market with AUTOBOLI LTD today.

Access Real-Time Data Instantly

Gain immediate access to live auction data across the UK. Filter by region, vehicle type, or auction house to find exactly what you need as soon as it’s listed.

Make Smarter Decisions

Get essential information like auction locations, vehicle details, conditions, and bidding results. Use analytics tools in Gold and Platinum plans to track trends, find deals, and refine your buying strategy.

This data is crucial for making fast decisions in a competitive market, and with our service, you’ll never miss a valuable opportunity.
